---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="How It Works | Links AI"
  description="A clear look at how Links AI works: assess the workflow, build the system, launch it, and improve it over time."
  pageClass="page-how-it-works"
>
  <section class="hero" slot="hero">
    <h1>How it works</h1>
    <p>
      We keep this simple: understand the workflow, build the right system,
      launch it in the real business, and keep improving it over time.
    </p>
    <a class="btn" href="/contact">Get in touch</a>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>The process</h2>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <span class="step-num">01</span>
        <h3>We look at how the work happens today</h3>
        <p>We learn where requests come in, where things get stuck, who has to touch them, and where follow-up breaks down.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <span class="step-num">02</span>
        <h3>We choose the best place to start</h3>
        <p>We define a practical first project with clear scope, expected impact, and a realistic path to launch.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <span class="step-num">03</span>
        <h3>We build and launch it with your team</h3>
        <p>We implement the system in your real environment, test it against live workflows, and make sure it works in practice.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <span class="step-num">04</span>
        <h3>We improve it as the business learns</h3>
        <p>After launch, we refine the workflow, improve reliability, and expand the system when it is proving value.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>What you can hire us for</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Workflow assessment</h3>
        <p>If you are not sure where AI fits yet, we can review the operation with you and identify the strongest place to start.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Build and launch</h3>
        <p>If you already know the workflow you want to improve, we can design and implement the first working system.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Ongoing support</h3>
        <p>If you want the system to keep getting better after launch, we can stay involved to monitor, refine, and expand it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>What to expect from us</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Clear communication</h3>
        <p>You should know what we are building, what comes next, and how the work is performing.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Practical decisions</h3>
        <p>We do not push AI for its own sake. We focus on solving operational problems in a way your team can actually use.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>A path beyond the first project</h3>
        <p>We start with one useful workflow, then expand only when the first system is working and worth building on.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-box">
    <h2>Want to talk through your workflow?</h2>
    <p>Tell us what is repetitive, manual, or hard to keep up with, and we will help you figure out the right next step.</p>
    <a class="btn" href="/contact">Get in touch</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
